decks.notes: The main focus of this deck is to quickly assemble key combo pieces such as Tinker, Time Vault, and Mystic Forge to generate a powerful engine with Paradoxical Outcome. Utilizing fast mana sources like Mishra's Workshop and Mana Crypt, the deck aims to generate significant card advantage and mana efficiency to overwhelm the opponent. With control elements such as Force of Will and Grim Monolith, along with disruptive spells like Sink into Stupor, the deck looks to disrupt the opponent's game plan while executing its own combo to secure a victory.
